---
title: North Indian Style Beef Mince and Pea Curry with Basmati Rice and Cashew Nuts
description: This North Indian Style Beef Mince and Pea Curry is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/north-indian-style-beef-mince-and-pea-curry-8e408428-553fade1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/north-indian-style-beef-mince-and-pea-curry-628211f65d4c0a51b20b540d-881ee419.pdf
author: Anushka Magan
time required: 30 minutes
